gugu and andile is a 2008 south african drama film directed by minky schlesinger , and starring daphney hlomuka , neil mccarthy & lungelo dhladhla .   the film received 10 nominations and won 3 awards at the 2009 africa movie academy awards , including the awards for best film in an african language , most promising actor and most promising actress .   it was also a competitor in the best tv feature category at the 2009 fespaco film festival in burkina faso , the oldest and largest film festival on the african continent .   the story is set in south africa in 1993 , during the upheaval in the struggle for democracy .   a sixteen-year-old zulu boy gugu is in love with a xhosa girl andile , against the wishes of their respective communities .